  1  SELECT STU_ID,PID,COMPANY,P.CITY,S.NAME,BNAME,CNAME, SB1.SNAME SUBJECT1,SB2.SNAME SUBJECT2,SB3.SNAME SUBJECT3
  2  FROM PLACEMENTS P,STUDENTS S, BATCHES B, COURSES C ,SUBJECTS SB1,SUBJECTS SB2,SUBJECTS SB3
  3  WHERE S.STU_ID = P.STID(+) AND S.B_ID = B.BID AND B.CID = C.CID AND SID1 = SB1.SID AND SID2 = SB2.SID AND SID3 = SB3.SID
  4* ORDER BY 1

COLUMN   VALUE_COL_PLUS_SHOW_SPPARAM ON
HEADING  'VALUE'
FORMAT   a28
word_wrap 

COLUMN   NAME_COL_PLUS_SHOW_SPPARAM ON
HEADING  'NAME'
FORMAT   a29
word_wrap

HEADING  'VALUE'
FORMAT   a30

COLUMN   name_col_plus_show_param ON
HEADING  'NAME'
FORMAT   a36

COLUMN   units_col_plus_show_sga ON
FORMAT   a15

COLUMN   name_col_plus_show_sga ON
FORMAT   a24

COLUMN   ERROR ON
FORMAT   A65
word_wrap

FORMAT   A8

FORMAT   A15
